dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Anthony Flores. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Amber Allen.
Nice to meet you, Amber. Can you please provide your policy number for verification purposes?
Of course, my policy number is two three four five six.
Thank you, Amber. Could you also confirm your date of birth for additional verification?
My date of birth is zero four dash one two dash one nine eight seven.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about your policy today, Amber?
I'm just checking on the status of a recent claim I filed.
I will look into that for you. Thank you for your patience, Amber.
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance today, Amber. Have a great day!
